Package: libtrigger
Version: 1.0.0-1
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Tony B <krakjn@gmail.com>
Architecture: any
Depends: libc6
Description: Cross-platform file watching library
 A C library for watching files and directories for changes
 and calling callbacks when events occur. Supports both
 macOS (kqueue) and Linux (inotify) platforms. 
